    • Method Detail

      • load

        TestSet load(File file)
        Parses a TAP File. Note: this method only works if the TapConsumer was constructed with an assumed character set encoding, and file really is encoded in that assumed encoding. For a more flexible approach, the caller (who should know best about the encoding of any given input file) should have already wrapped the file in an InputStreamReader, and should pass that to load(Readable).
        Parameters:
        file - TAP File.
        Returns:
        TestSet
        Throws:
        TapConsumerException
